{
  "id": "60e05c90f88ed500223a830e",
  "title": "履歴スライダー",
  "created": 1625316499,
  "updated": 1772274451,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "60e05c90f88ed500223a830e",
      "text": "履歴スライダー",
      "userId": "60d7d3e32182b900220b8719",
      "created": 1625316499,
      "updated": 1625316499
    },
    {
      "id": "69a2348b0000000000c20448",
      "text": " Cosenseの過去の編集履歴を眺める[UserScript]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772237963,
      "updated": 1772238127
    },
    {
      "id": "69a2363100000000003fdb0e",
      "text": " Page Historyより細かい編集履歴を確認できる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772238385,
      "updated": 1772238385
    },
    {
      "id": "69a235a200000000003fdb0c",
      "text": " ページの文章を間違って消してしまったときに便利。もとの文章がわかるので。",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772238243,
      "updated": 1772238392
    },
    {
      "id": "69a234fd00000000003fdb0a",
      "text": " Scriptの変遷：[/scrapboxlab/編集履歴を知る]→[/hogashi-pub/履歴スライダー](→[履歴スライダー])→[/takker/scrapbox-commit-viewer]→[/takker/scrapbox-commit-viewer-2]→[/takker/scrapbox-commit-viewer@0.2.0]→[/takker/scrapbox-commit-viewer@0.2.0], [/programming-notes/scrapbox-history-slider@0.2.0]→[/programming-notes/scrapbox-history-slider@0.2.1]→[/takker/scrapbox-history-slider]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772238078,
      "updated": 1772239284
    },
    {
      "id": "69a239b400000000003fdb19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772239285,
      "updated": 1772239285
    },
    {
      "id": "60e06056dd60be0000427230",
      "text": "恐ろしいレベルの解像度で履歴が残っていて恐ろしい()[45Nuyagawa.icon]",
      "userId": "5fe444046f8e560041dd60be",
      "created": 1625317463,
      "updated": 1625317486
    },
    {
      "id": "60e19ae31280f0000010ca96",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/5d526a6c3137c2dfd51be9cdd6371a0f]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1625397989,
      "updated": 1625397990
    },
    {
      "id": "60e19b051280f0000010ca98",
      "text": " 上図は[/programming-notes/scrapbox-history-slider@0.2.1]のcapture",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1625398023,
      "updated": 1625398041
    },
    {
      "id": "60e06b661280f00000d0d568",
      "text": "よく使う。便利[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1625320295,
      "updated": 1625320305
    },
    {
      "id": "60e05c920b87190000703dc2",
      "text": " たくさん[undo]したあと間違えて文字を打ってredoできなくなったとき",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1625316499,
      "updated": 1625320356
    },
    {
      "id": "60e06b811280f00000d0d569",
      "text": " 編集中に別ページへのリンクを押しちゃってundoできなくなったとき",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1625320322,
      "updated": 1625320408
    },
    {
      "id": "60e06bd91280f00000d0d56a",
      "text": " 別の端末で編集した内容をundoしたいとき",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1625320409,
      "updated": 1625320439
    },
    {
      "id": "60e06bf71280f00000d0d56b",
      "text": " [Page History]に残っていない直近の細かい編集履歴をみたいとき",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1625320440,
      "updated": 1625320484
    },
    {
      "id": "60e06a001280f00000d0d567",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1625319937,
      "updated": 1625319937
    },
    {
      "id": "60f6c19a79d3a9000044f165",
      "text": "うっかり書いてしまったハズい記述もバレてしまう可能性がありそうだｗ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1626784154,
      "updated": 1626784193
    },
    {
      "id": "60f6c19e79d3a9000044f166",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1626784159,
      "updated": 1626784159
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60c041280f000004b7938",
      "text": "↓で発見した",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737668,
      "updated": 1626737673
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b7928",
      "text": "from [2021/03/31]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b792a",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737653
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b792b",
      "text": " なんだこのUserScript！？(驚愕)",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b792c",
      "text": "   [/discordjs-japan/Aiueokashi#6052a4033760e90000799f21]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b792d",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/9c7af29d5c09e55c258634cb070ce0ac]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b792e",
      "text": "  [Scrapboxのcommit]をすっごくわかりやすく表示してくれる！",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b792f",
      "text": "   早速[- パクって]参考にしてUserScript作るか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b7930",
      "text": "   [/icons2/へえ〜.icon][yosider.icon][kuuote.icon][U.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b7931",
      "text": "   　ぱっと見意味がわからなかった",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b7932",
      "text": "   　Scrapboxってユーザー側にコミットの塊投げてるのか[kuuote.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b7933",
      "text": "   　 Undoとかちゃんとやるならその方がいいか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b7934",
      "text": "  編集の経緯がとても細かくわかってしまう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
    {
      "id": "60f60be31280f000004b7935",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/a3bb167c46dd47a3d550700261c0a91b]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1626737634,
      "updated": 1626737634
    },
